728120f-a.title: Queens: Union Turnpike - Vleigh Place
728120f-a.text:
Union Turnpike (foreground), at the N.E. corner of Vleigh Place (the Head of the Vleigh Road, left), showing an old farm house belonging to B. Laddy in 1873 and D. Letty in 1891.

April 1929.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
